{"tid":2235341,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"失敗者","createTime":"2020-10-08T14:51:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T23:02:56.000Z","uid":124514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"50f33c25f674d565a42df489da08150da80ebab9","tid":2235341,"uid":124514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T14:51:56.000Z","msg":"有朋友有男朋友又點<br />\n一啲都唔覺得自己開心<br />\n返工返得好辛苦<br />\n同佢地講都係叫我呢個時勢唔好辭職<br />\n雖然都知佢地係俾忠告我<br />\n但係我真係返到成日一個人匿埋喊<br />\n好辛苦好辛苦好辛苦<br />\n我覺得冇人明白我<br />\n<br />\n朋友同我打同一份工<br />\n佢就返到好輕鬆<br />\n我就返到好壓抑<br />\n佢炒股就贏大錢<br />\n我炒股就輸大錢<br />\n唔係想比較<br />\n但聽到就覺得自己好loser<br />\n<br />\n有時真係好想匿埋自己一個算<br />\n完全唔想見人<br />\n男朋友朋友都唔想見"},{"pid":"e3d881b65365136b42a54834844f34e4c1ab4cbe","tid":2235341,"uid":219842,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T14:52:55.000Z","msg":"好少見女仔炒股票"},{"pid":"7badb6d182460d0aca229658bea0e6a377798157","tid":2235341,"uid":171451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T14:53:08.000Z","msg":"先喜歡你自己好嗎"},{"pid":"b3a00ed25a0b4e9e02035090ba186478e87201e3","tid":2235341,"uid":318952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T14:54:52.000Z","msg":"我試過400萬一鋪清袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9459f2057d2f7209bdc31bc53a26d038b5ce5ce","tid":2235341,"uid":142313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T15:07:05.000Z","msg":"試吓跟佢炒股<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a52b5bf19718dbe9f3632746e755b55f1a6bf737","tid":2235341,"uid":124514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7badb6d182460d0aca229658bea0e6a377798157","tid":2235341,"uid":171451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T14:53:08.000Z","msg":"先喜歡你自己好嗎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T15:07:11.000Z","msg":"做乜都差過人<br />\n點喜歡自己"},{"pid":"4236eb6acc43ff83bad5aeeea46bd2077709d440","tid"